frames.caption: A majestic, mythical creature with glowing fur strides across a starlit landscape. The creature's luminous presence illuminates the ground, creating a magical aura. Stars twinkle in the night sky, enhancing the enchanting atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fantastical setting with a mythical creature walking through a starlit landscape. The creature's glowing fur casts light on the ground, creating a surreal and magical environment.

frames.caption: A majestic, mythical creature resembling a lion with glowing fur stands under a starry sky. Its luminous body casts a warm, golden light on the ground, creating an ethereal glow around it. The creature appears powerful and otherworldly, set against the vastness of the cosmos.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fantastical setting where a mythical creature, akin to a lion, is illuminated by its own radiant glow. It stands on a barren landscape under a clear, star-filled sky, suggesting a mystical or dreamlike environment.
